name: Super Yeti #100
description: SuperYeti is a 3D collection of randomized characters created through a standard ERC-721 contract and backed by IPFS file storage and registered on the Ethereum Blockchain. Future implementation of a multiplayer, play-to-earn game where SuperYetis own land, breed and compete with one another to protect the Yetiverse. You can learn more at www.superyeti.co
